# Paper 1.8.8 JAR Configuration

This configuration file is meant to document the settings and options available when running a Paper 1.8.8 server.

## General Configuration
- **server-name**: The name of your server as it will appear in the server list.
- **max-players**: The maximum number of players that can join the server at the same time.
- **motd**: Message of the day that will be displayed in the server list.

## Performance Settings
- **view-distance**: Determines how many chunks the server will load around players.
- **ticking-area**: Allows you to define an area in which entities will continue to tick, regardless of player presence.

## Plugins Configuration
- **plugins-folder**: The folder where server plugins are stored.

## Console Settings
- **console-display-name**: The display name of the console in the server logs.

For more specific options and configurations, please refer to the official Paper Spigot documentation or relevant community resources.